<br>
I dislike EQ's continuing emphasis on content designed solely for Uber-guilds.  I assumed EQ was mainly for groups/soloing when I first started playing.  I had fun doing raids for a while, but at this point doing endless timesink style raiding/exp grinding is very little fun, and I think EQ has gone too far in the wrong direction for too long.  <br>
